  "raw_html": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"is-tensor\">\n<span id=\"api-paddle-is-tensor\"></span>\n<h1>is_tensor<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#is-tensor\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\"></a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">paddle.</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">is_tensor</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span>\n<em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">x</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Any</span></span></em>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span>\n<span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">TypeGuard</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">Tensor</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span></span>\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/blob/release/3.3/python/paddle/tensor/logic.py#L975\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a>\n</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>Tests whether input object is a paddle.Tensor.</p>\n<div class=\"admonition note\">\n<p class=\"admonition-title\">Note</p>\n<p>Alias Support: The parameter name <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">obj</span></code> can be used as an alias for <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">x</span></code>. For example, <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">is_tensor(obj=tensor_x)</span></code> is equivalent to <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">is_tensor(x=tensor_x)</span></code>.</p>\n</div>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">\n           Parameters\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\">\n<p><strong>x</strong> (<em>object</em>) – Object to test. alias: <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">obj</span></code>.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt class=\"field-even\">\n           Returns\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-even\">\n<p>A boolean value. True if <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">x</span></code> is a paddle.Tensor, otherwise False.</p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p class=\"rubric\">Examples</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\">\n<div class=\"highlight\">\n<pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">paddle</span>\n\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">input1</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rand</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">shape</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"p\">],</span> <span class=\"n\">dtype</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'float32'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">is_tensor</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">input1</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">check</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"go\">True</span>\n\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">input3</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">4</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\